    doNewSend(["33", [boostDir]]);
}

var repeater = function(key, action, interval) {
    let _isKeyDown = false;
    let _intervalId = undefined;

    return {
        start(keycode) {
            if(keycode == key && document.activeElement.id.toLowerCase() !== 'chatbox') {
                _isKeyDown = true;
                if(_intervalId === undefined) {
                    _intervalId = setInterval(() => {
                        action();
                        if(!_isKeyDown){
                            clearInterval(_intervalId);
                            _intervalId = undefined;
                            console.log("claered");
                        }
                    }, interval);
                }
            }
        },

        stop(keycode) {
            if(keycode == key && document.activeElement.id.toLowerCase() !== 'chatbox') {
                _isKeyDown = false;
            }
        }
    };


}

function toRad(angle) {
    return angle * 0.01745329251;
}

function dist(a, b){
    return Math.sqrt( Math.pow((b.y-a[2]), 2) + Math.pow((b.x-a[1]), 2) );
}

function lol(space, chance) {
   let result = '';
   let characters;
   if(space) {
       characters = ach1;
   }
   if(space) {
       characters = characters.padStart((30 - characters.length) / 2 + characters.length)
       characters = characters.padEnd(30);
   }
   let count = 0;
   for (let i = 0; i < characters.length; i++ ) {
      if(Math.floor(Math.random() * chance) == 0 && characters.charAt(i) != "-" && count < 0 && characters.charAt(i) != " ") {
          result += "";
          count++
      } else {
          result += characters.charAt(i);
      }
   }
   return result;
}

(function() {
  var UPDATE_DELAY = 700;

  var lastUpdate = 0;
  var frames = 0;

  var displayElement = document.createElement("div");
  displayElement.style.padding = "5px";
  displayElement.style.font = "80px Arial";
  displayElement.style.display = "block";
  displayElement.style.position = "fixed";
  displayElement.style.top = "1000px";
  displayElement.style.left = "0px";
  displayElement.textContent = "Calculating...";
  document.body.appendChild(displayElement);

  function cssColorToRGB(color) {
    var values;

    if (color.startsWith("rgba")) {
      values = color.substring(5, color.length - 1).split(",");
    } else if (color.startsWith("rgb")) {
      values = color.substring(4, color.length - 1).split(",");
    } else if (color.startsWith("#") && color.length === 4) {
      values = [];
      values[0] = "" + parseInt("0x" + color.substr(1, 1));
      values[1] = "" + parseInt("0x" + color.substr(2, 1));
      values[2] = "" + parseInt("0x" + color.substr(3, 1));
    } else if (color.startsWith("#") && color.length === 7) {
      values = [];
      values[0] = "" + parseInt("0x" + color.substr(1, 2));
      values[1] = "" + parseInt("0x" + color.substr(3, 2));
      values[2] = "" + parseInt("0x" + color.substr(5, 2));
    } else {
      return {r : 255, g : 255, b : 255};
    }

    return {
      r : Number(values[0]),
      g : Number(values[1]),
      b : Number(values[2])
    };
  }

  function getInvertedRGB(values) {
    return "rgb(" + (255 - values.r) + "," + (9 - values.g) + ","
      + (9 - values.b) + ")";
  }

  function getOpaqueRGB(values) {
    return "rgba(" + values.r + "," + values.g + "," + values.b + ",0.7)";
  }

  function updateCounter() {
    var bgColor = getComputedStyle(document.body, null).getPropertyValue(
      "background-color");
    var bgColorValues = cssColorToRGB(bgColor);
    var textColor = getInvertedRGB(bgColorValues);
    var displayBg = getOpaqueRGB(bgColorValues);
    displayElement.style.color = "#a20ffd";
    displayElement.style.background = displayBg;

    var now = Date.now();
    var elapsed = now - lastUpdate;
    if (elapsed < UPDATE_DELAY) {
      ++frames;
    } else {
      var fps = Math.round(frames / (elapsed / 1000));
      displayElement.textContent = fps + " FPS";
      frames = 0;
      lastUpdate = now;
    }

    requestAnimationFrame(updateCounter);
  }

  lastUpdate = Date.now();
  requestAnimationFrame(updateCounter);
})();

document.querySelector("#ping-display-2").appendChild(
  (function() {
    let oldPing = 0;
    let text = "Ping (ms): ";
    const pingSpan = document.createElement("span"); //720000
    pingSpan.id = "pingTime";
    pingSpan.textContent = text;
    pingSpan.style.display = "block";
    setInterval(function() {
      typeof pingTime !== "undefined" &&
        oldPing !== pingTime &&
        ((oldPing = pingTime),
        (pingSpan.textContent = text + oldPing),
        (function() {
          if (oldPing <= 30) {
            document.getElementById('ping-display-3').innerHTML = '';
            document.getElementById('ping-display-3').style.color = 'cyan';
            pingSpan.style.color = "cyan";
          }
          if (oldPing >= 31 && oldPing <= 100) {
            document.getElementById('ping-display-3').innerHTML = '';
            document.getElementById('ping-display-3').style.color = 'lime';
            pingSpan.style.color = "lime";
          }
          if (oldPing >= 101 && oldPing <= 125) {
            document.getElementById('ping-display-3').innerHTML = '';
            document.getElementById('ping-display-3').style.color = '#7db304';
            pingSpan.style.color = "#7db304";
          }
          if (oldPing >= 126 && oldPing <= 155) {
            document.getElementById('ping-display-3').innerHTML = '';
            document.getElementById('ping-display-3').style.color = '#cfcc03';
            pingSpan.style.color = "#cfcc03";
          }
          if (oldPing >= 156 && oldPing <= 200) {
           document.getElementById('ping-display-3').innerHTML = '';
           document.getElementById('ping-display-3').style.color = '#c1e401';
           pingSpan.style.color = "#c1e401";
          }
          if (oldPing >= 201 && oldPing <= 275) {
           document.getElementById('ping-display-3').innerHTML = '';
           document.getElementById('ping-display-3').style.color = 'yellow';
           pingSpan.style.color = "yellow";
          }
          if (oldPing >= 276 && oldPing <= 350) {
           document.getElementById('ping-display-3').innerHTML = '';
           document.getElementById('ping-display-3').style.color = '#e66d02';
           pingSpan.style.color = "#e66d02";
          }
          if (oldPing >= 351 && oldPing <= 500) {
           document.getElementById('ping-display-3').innerHTML = '';
           document.getElementById('ping-display-3').style.color = '#ff3203';
           pingSpan.style.color = "#ff3203";
          }
          if (oldPing >= 501 && oldPing <= 850) {
           document.getElementById('ping-display-3').innerHTML = '';
           pingSpan.style.color = "#f00";
          }
          if (oldPing >= 851 && oldPing <= 1500) {
           document.getElementById('ping-display-3').innerHTML = '';
           document.getElementById('ping-display-3').style.color = '#cc0000';
           pingSpan.style.color = "#cc0000";
          }
          if (oldPing >= 1501 && oldPing <= 2350) {
           document.getElementById('ping-display-3').innerHTML = '';
           document.getElementById('ping-display-3').style.color = '#990000';
           pingSpan.style.color = "#990000";
          }
          if (oldPing >= 2351 && oldPing <= 4000) {
           document.getElementById('ping-display-3').innerHTML = '';
           document.getElementById('ping-display-3').style.color = '#660000';
           pingSpan.style.color = "#660000";
          }
          if (oldPing >= 4001 && oldPing <= 40000) {
           pingSpan.style.color = "#660000";
          }
          if (oldPing >= 200 && oldPing <= 40000) {
           doNewSend(["ch", ["Warning: " + oldPing + " ms"]]);
          }
        })());
    });
    return pingSpan;
  })()
);
